The ramen was exceptionally tasty and delicious, with just the right amount of fat. Despite looking like a small portion, it was surprisingly filling. A minor drawback is that you have to pay extra for an egg and spicy sauce.

A fun addition was the Japanese toilet with all its buttons and settings, adding a unique touch to the overall experience.'}

